I refuse to listen to this song. I bless copyright now and only now for allowing my ears to keep clean.
I was tempted to listen because Jungkook tweeted about it,, but I couldn't do it.
I found myself shaking in fear with just the thought of it. Bile rose up my throat when I accidentally watched a cringy tik tok with the song.
Now, I know I'm being mean but don't get me wrong I don't hate Justin. I just don't like him. I am allowed not to like someone.
Just looking at this song's lyrics I can tell he no longer enjoys doing what he does. I mean, out of all the things why did he have to say this was for his wife?
I know nothing about Hailey but to have a song about you that just says "you have that yummy yum" must not...be something you would expect from your singer husband.
